snippet.textDisplay: If medical professionals & legal professionals are going "rogue" against their government, then we should be listening.  They both know the risks associated with what they were doing but were willing to risk it so that the rest of the world knew the truth.  So anybody saying that unless we live there, we have no idea what we're talking about, we know that 4-6 of the worst plague-like animal-human viruses have come out of your country and killed thousands of people.  More each time a new strain comes out.  We all have many of your countrymen living in our countries as citizens ad even more visiting as tourists each year.  A lot of our countries now have mounting numbers of infected people.  I have watched this via media since it first was reported, which was closer to the end of December rather than the beginning as is now said to be the case.  I have watched the numbers of infection and deaths pretty much double by the day x 2.  There are thousands dead now and its only 16Feb.  End of January, 100 turned to 280 turned to 400 within 5 days.  Our own govts didnt close borders to travel until end of Jan.  Thats how we got our own cases manifest.  Chinese NY meant more travel btw there and our countries.   Clearly the govt there in China thinks the rest of the world can be on a "needs to know basis"......and is selective in their "truth".   We will never know the truth because the commos dont share anything.  The whistleblowers are disappearing (dead?  jailed?  assassinated?) under suspicious circumstances and the commos wont acknowledge or reveal why or where.   If they had nothing to hide, they'd be transparent.  They arent.  So the rest of the world is now in damage control and isolating your country so it can eat itself inside out until (if) this thing is contained, or it kills its entire population....whichever comes first.   The mind boggles on the conditions and hows and whys an animal borne disease transfers to a human and then kills them....but its China's specialty. They can keep it and their secrets.
